{"tid":2505373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟兩大重臣: 「中共」和歐盟有著根本分歧. 歐盟必須跟美國政府合作.","createTime":"2021-04-26T14:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T17:29:07.000Z","uid":134071,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"06855403aca3497f340d6a8de464a91d49268c4f","tid":2505373,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"馮德萊恩=歐盟執委會主席<br />\n博雷爾=歐盟外交與安全政策高級代表<br />\n<br />\n據politico報道，馮德萊恩和博雷爾在給歐盟27國領導人的信中說，北京正在經歷&quot;威權主義的轉向&quot;。他們說，歐盟和中國有 &quot;根本分歧&quot;，&quot;不能掩蓋蒙混過關&quot;。&quot;我們必須接受[拜登]的開放邀請之手&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wstv_lizzi/status/1386416183272902658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwstv_lizzi%2Fstatus%2F1386416183272902658&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6xSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=41bd39f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwstv_lizzi%2Fstatus%2F1386416183272902658&h=09fb4512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/wstv_lizzi/status/1386416183272902658</a>"},{"pid":"566342c23eb5c2376bcebb89b01216633178a017","tid":2505373,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"已fact check, 有原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.eu/article/eu-china-biden-economy-climate-europe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Feu-china-biden-economy-climate-europe%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6xSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=839805c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.eu/article/eu-china-biden-economy-climate-europe/</a>"},{"pid":"b5c6b409278f7574776414cc45e1e96a23ecff1a","tid":2505373,"uid":309558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"566342c23eb5c2376bcebb89b01216633178a017","tid":2505373,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"已fact check, 有原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.eu/article/